This works, but is a terrible way to pack a game. It will take ~2hrs+ to extract, because it's a solid archive with a 64K dictionary size. Ridiculous. Learn how to compress, webchella. You only make a solid archive if you're compressing the exact same kind of file, like text, not a random mix of already-compressed binary files and text files. Extracting a solid archive is extremely slow compared to a regular archive, and coupled with the tiny dictionary size makes it worse.  Also, any corruption in the archive makes all data that follows that corruption corrupt, as well. To anyone else, d/l this from the other torrent.
